===Conjunction===
'''when'''

# at what time.
#: ''They were told '''when''' to sleep''.
# at such time as.
#: ''I’m happiest '''when''' I’m working''.
# as soon as.
#: ''I’ll do it '''when''' I get the time''.
# at a time in the past
#: ''It was raining '''when''' I came yesterday''.

